Citation.sTitle: Solubilities of 1,1'-(Ethane-1,2-diyl)-bis(pyridinium) Dihexafluorophosphate in Aqueous Acetone Mixtures
Citation.sAbstract: Using a laser monitoring technique, the solubilities of 1,1'-(ethane-1,2-diyl)-bis(pyridinium) dihexafluorophosphate in binary acetone + water solvent mixtures were determined at temperatures from (290.15 to 327.45) K at atmospheric pressure. The experimental data were well correlated with the modified Apelblat equation.
